Can't think of a gift for a newborn Photographer?
How about a gift certificate from The Knitting Bitty?
Comes in denominations to suit ALL budgets!

Conditions of Gift Certificates:
A redemption code will be issued with each gift certificate. Gift certificates are issued in USD currency only. Gift certificates may be used for custom orders as well as items that are currently listed in the shop. There is no expiration date for gift certificates. Remaining balance on gift certificates may not be exchanged for cash or money, but may be used towards another order. Holder of gift card is responsible for the redemption code- please keep your redemption code in a safe place.
